_sText:
Well, after I uploaded BA_Jail_Claustrum a few hours ago, I realized it was packed with errors. Well, now all those errors are fixed, and a few extra features have been added. Here is what this whole map has:
-Execution Room
-Vent Complex
-Breakable Escape Points
-Escape Routes
-Lockdown System
-Cafeteria
-Soccer Field/Arena
-Swimming Pool
-Solitary Confinement
-CT Armory
-T Armory
-And more stuff that I can't remember off the top of my head
